items.headline: Tune into the Jet Set Radio Wiki
items.desc: Jet Set Radio is the funkiest, fleshiest radio station out there. Turn that dial to hear some of the grooviest tunes around. Get caught up on the happenin's with Professor K while your crew tags the city and keeps the other taggers at bay. The Jet Radio wiki has several informational articles and pages about Jet Set Radio and Jet Set Radio Future.t
